comments: Improv and sketch comedy. Normally a great teacher, but would always use me as an example of what not to be. COME BACK! <3 Chip

This was the hardest A at Xavier. While it was usually easy to understand, the teacher always held a cup in her hand, which was distracting. She thinks she is really funny though. But, sometimes she gets upset and it gets really awkward in the room. She is very very good looking though and is worth taking the class for her looks. seriously.

Aside from the fact that she yelled at me EVERYDAY for how i held my imaginary objects she was cool. but it really ticked me off when she took 50 points off when I had to leave early cause i had the flu. ask her about Milford.
